Hollywood. 
</P>
<P>
 Hours: Doors open 7 p.m., music from 9 p.m. New Year's Eve. 
</P>
<P>
 Price: $50, special dinner menu, two drinks included, champagne toast. 
</P>
<P>
 Call: (818) 980-1615. 
</P>
