lights 39,000 Neighborhood park renovations Mission Viejo 33,000 Various park 
improvements 27,500 Irrigation conversion Orange 75,000 Santa Fe depot park 
5,000 Handy Park 100,000 Belmont (Southridge) Park Orange Unified 100,000 Ana 
Hills School Schl. Distr. field lighting 150,000 Modular rec structures 
