</P>
<P>
 It was the first loss of the season for the Bears (7-1).  
</P>
<P>
 Faulkner had missed a free throw late in regulation to help Cal force 
overtime. 
</P>
<P>
 * 
</P>
<P>
 No. 1 North Carolina 98, Old Dominion 79 -- Jerry Stackhouse was nine for nine 
from the field and four for four from the free-throw line in the first half to 
lead the Tar Heels at Norfolk, Va. 
</P>
<P>
 Stackhouse finished with 29 points for North Carolina (8-0). Old Dominion is 
5-6. 
</P>
<P>
 * 
</P>
<P>
 No. 3 Arkansas 84, No. 20 Cincinnati 75 -- Corliss Williamson scored 27 points 
and Scotty Thurman 20 as the Razorbacks (10-1) overcame the Bearcats (8-4) in 
final of the Rainbow Classic in Honolulu. 
</P>
<P>
 * 
</P>
<P>
