 Joey Ramirez made two free throws with 11.1 seconds left to secure 
Pepperdine's 61-55 victory over Eastern Kentucky on Thursday night in the 
consolation game of the Hoosier Classic. 
</P>
<P>
 After Ramirez made both shots, teammate Monte Marcaccini made one of two free 
throws with 3.8 seconds left for the final score. 
