(2-9). 
</P>
<P>
 Canyon 70, Sonora 64 -- Aiyana Nash's career-high 47 for Sonora (2-8) was 
overshadowed by Robynn Kuhlmann's 32 points and Unelda Sweet's school-record 30 
rebounds for Canyon (8-6). 
</P>
