basketball team in 1990, was sentenced to two years in prison for his role in a 
carjacking. 
</P>
<P>
 Scurry and co-defendant Kevin Williams pleaded guilty last month to felony 
charges in connection with a carjacking in which the victim was shot. 
</P>
<P>
 Scurry was a key player in UNLV's 103-73 victory over Duke in the 1990 
national championship game. He played professionally for a while in Japan, then 
moved back to Las Vegas. 
</P>
